citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:45 pm on
November 28, 2023. The inspector knocked on the door and called the numbers on file. The licensee called back but
stated they were not available to conduct an inspection today.
End Section
